        width: 160
        height: 30
    - id: 36
      fields:
      - title: Title
        value: 
        type: 0
        typeString: 
      - title: Description
        value: 
        type: 0
        typeString: 
      - title: Actor
        value: 7
        type: 0
        typeString: CustomFieldType_Actor
      - title: Conversant
        value: 7
        type: 0
        typeString: CustomFieldType_Actor
      - title: Menu Text
        value: 
        type: 0
        typeString: 
      - title: Dialogue Text
        value: Not to mention the added burden of funeral arrangements, for example.
          Talking about death in advance-and perhaps even making thoughtful, informed
          preparations  can spare you a great deal of heartbreak later. It gives
          you the space to grieve more peacefully when the time comes.
        type: 0
        typeString: 
      - title: Sequence
        value: 
        type: 0
        typeString: 
      conversationID: 1
      isRoot: 0
      isGroup: 0
      nodeColor: 
      delaySimStatus: 0
